// Regression: a bare `return` in top-level (script-mode) code compiled into the
// synthesized `long long wyn_main()` as `return;` → C error "non-void function
// should return a value". codegen_program now sets current_fn_c_nonvoid while
// emitting the synthesized main, so a bare return lowers to `return 0;`. (2026-07)
print("start")
if 1 == 1 {
    print("early")
    return
}
print("late")
// EXPECT: start
// EXPECT: early
